@page
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.TagHelpers
@using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore
@using UniversityMedicalRecord.Data
@using UniversityMedicalRecord.Models
@model UnivMedicalRecord.Pages.Homepage.EditRecord



    @{
	    Layout = null;
    }


<style>

body {
    background-color: #8080;
    font-family: sans-serif;
}

form {
    background-color: #fff;
    width: 1000px;
    max-width: max-content;
    max-height: max-content;
    margin: 50px auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    box-shadow: 2px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

h3 {
    color: #333;
}

table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

table, th, td {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
}

th, td {
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: left;
}

label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    font-size: 16px;
}

input, select {
    width: calc(100% - 10px);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid black;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-right: 5px;
    margin-left: 5px;
}


button {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #555;
}
</style> 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"
          content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
	    Create General Records
    </title>
     <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ENjdO4Dr2bkBIFxQpeoTz1HIcje39Wm4jDKdf19U8gI4ddQ3GYNS7NTKfAdVQSZe" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
</head>

<div>
	<form class="mt-3" style="height: unset;  background-color: unset; padding: unset; margin: auto; box-shadow: unset; align-self: center" method="post">
		<div class="card" style="flex-direction: row; background-color: black; width: 1000px; align-items: center">
			<a href="#" class="nav-link text-white">
			<button class="btn btn-dark m-lg-3" asp-page-handler="Dashboard">Dashboard</button>
			<button class="btn btn-dark m-lg-3" asp-page-handler="Records">Records</button>
			</a>
		</div>
	</form>
</div>
  
<body>
<form method="post" style="width: auto">
	<input type="hidden" asp-for="Personal.Id"/>
	<input type="hidden" asp-for="FamilyInfo.Id"/>
	<input type="hidden" asp-for="Medical.Id"/>
	<div style="text-align: center">
		<h3>General Records</h3>
		<div>
			<b>
				<div class="mb-10" style="float:left">Personal Information</div></b>
			<br/>
			<table>
				<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td> <label for="name">Name*</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.Name" type="text" id="name">
					</td>
					<td> <label for="age">Age*</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.Age" type=number id="age">
					</td>
					<td>
                        <div class="mt-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                            <label class="me-3">Gender*</label>
                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input asp-for="Personal.Sex" type="radio" value="Male" id="radio1" class="form-check-input">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="radio1">Male</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input asp-for="Personal.Sex" type="radio" value="Female" id="radio2" class="form-check-input">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="radio2">Female</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </td>

				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td> <label for="email">Email</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.Email" type=text id="email">
					</td>
					<td> <label for="id">ID*</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.IdNumber" type=text id="id">
					</td>
					<td> <label for="mobile">Mobile</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.MobileNumber" type=text id="mobile">
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td> <label for="doctor">Doctor</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.PersonalDoctor" type=text id="doctor">
					</td>
					<td> <label for="insurance">Insurance</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.Insurance" type="text" id="insurance">
					</td>
					<td> <label for="dob">Date of Birth*</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.DateOfBirth" type=date id="dob">
					</td>

				</tr>
				<tr>

					<td> <label for="birthplace">Place of Birth</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.PlaceOfBirth" type="text" id="birthplace">
					</td>
					<td> <label for="address">Address*</label>
						<input asp-for="Personal.Address" type="text" id="address">
					</td>
				</tr>

				</tbody>
			</table>

		</div>
	</div>

	<br/>

	<b>
		<div style="float:left">Mother Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="motherName">Mother's Name</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherName" type="text" id="motherName">
			</td>
			<td> <label for="motherAddress">Mother's Address</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherAddress" type=text id="motherAddress">
			</td>
			<td> <label for="motherOccupation">Mother's Occupation</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherOccupation" type=text id="motherOccupation">
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="motherNumber">Mother's Number</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherNumber" type="text" id="motherNumber">
			</td>
			<td>
                <div class="mt-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <label class="me-3">Mother's Civil Status:</label>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherStatus" value="Married" type="radio" id="motherRadio1" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="motherRadio1">Married</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherStatus" value="Single" type="radio" id="motherRadio2" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="motherRadio2">Single</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherStatus" value="Separated" type="radio" id="motherRadio3" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="motherRadio3">Separated</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.MotherStatus" value="Widowed" type="radio" id="motherRadio4" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="motherRadio4">Widowed</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>

		</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>

	<br/>
	<b>
		<div style="float:left">Father Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="fatherName">Father's Name</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherName" type="text" id="fatherName">
			</td>
			<td> <label for="fatherAddress">Father's Address</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherAddress" type=text id="fatherAddress">
			</td>
			<td> <label for="fatherOccupation">Father's Occupation</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherOccupation" type=text id="fatherOccupation">
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="fatherNumber">Father's Number</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherNumber" type="text" id="fatherNumber">
			</td>
			<td>
                <div class="mt-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <label class="me-3">Father's Civil Status: </label>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherStatus" value="Married" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Married</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherStatus" value="Single" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Single</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherStatus" value="Separated" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Separated</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.FatherStatus" value="Widowed" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Widowed</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>

		</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>
	<br/>

	<b>
		<div style="float:left">Guardian Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="guardianName">Guardian's Name</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianName" type="text" id="guardianName">
			</td>
			<td> <label for="guardianAddress">Guardian's Address</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianAddress" type=text id="guardianAddress">
			</td>
			<td> <label for="guardianOccupation">Guardian's Occupation</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianOccupation" type=text id="guardianOccupation">
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="guardianRelation">Guardian's Relation</label>
				<input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianRelation" type="text" id="guardianRelation">
			</td>
			<td>
                <div class="mt-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <label class="me-3">Guardian's Civil Status: </label>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianStatus" value="Married" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Married</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianStatus" value="Single" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Single</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianStatus" value="Separated" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Separated</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input asp-for="FamilyInfo.GuardianStatus" value="Widowed" type="radio" class="form-check-input">
                        <label class="form-check-label">Widowed</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>
		</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>

	<br>
	<b>
		<div style="float:left">Medical Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="allergy">Allergies</label>
				<input asp-for="Medical.Allergy" type="text" id="allergy">
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label for="illness">Illnesses</label>
				<input asp-for="Medical.Illness" type="text" id="illness">
			</td>
		</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>
	<button class="btn btn-dark mt-4" asp-page-handler="Update">Update</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>